    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the free demo for Hot Wax, the falling-block puzzle game where you place candles and then light them up to create slowly-unfolding chain reactions in a gloomy temple built to some unholy creature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo contains the first difficulty for two of the full game's six gamemodes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; In Ritual, reach a score of 6,666 to summon the temple's god.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; In Penance, puzzle away a mass of candles that periodically keeps growing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A run typically lasts a couple of minutes. This demo version has the first 6 unlockable colour palettes of the full game's 29. This demo also has 4 exclusive achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your save for the demo will be compatible with the full game, so you will keep your unlocks and highscores.</p>",
